track_notes: This is an easy walk to this summit. You must park on the Route des Borrels. (The acces to the forest could be forbidden in case of strong wind or fire risk). There are many path in this forest and you must watch carefully the map or gps, if you dont want to get lost and never find the summit. As usual bring a lot of water as it can be very hot in summertime. Plenty romm on summit and GSM coverage is OK.
Easy walk from the south, plenty of space to park Chemin des Maures.
